  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support for the Food &amp; Agriculture Organisation (FAO) Voices of the Hungry Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To establish a global monitoring system of food insecurity based on data from a world survey of people&#x2019;s experience of food insecurity. This will lead to improved methods and tools for the analysis of food insecurity data and an increased understanding of the conditions that lead to food insecurity, who and where the food insecure are and their coping strategies. This will give better evidence upon which DFID and other development organisations can base their decisions and target assistance.</narrative>
  </description>
